library(survival)

Load cohort data:

load('brca2116_dataset.RData')

Two objects:

  • expDat: normalised gene expression data (on log scale) from 2116 tumours Affymetrix arrays). Probe data have been collapsed to 12403 genes (gene symbols used as IDs).
  • sampleData: data relating to each sample:
    • dataSet: data set that the sample came from.
    • sampleNames: sample ID
    • LN.status: Lymph Node status (LN+/LN-)
    • ER.status: Estrogen Receptor status (ER+/ER-)
    • PgR.status: Progesterone Receptor status (PgR+/PgR-)
    • Grade: Tumour Grade (G1/G2/G3)
    • Size: Tumour size (mm)
    • Age: Patient age at diagnosis (years)
    • Subtype: Molecular subtype (Basal/ClaudinLow/Her2/LumA/LumB/Normal/NoSubtype)
    • EndocrineTrt: Did patient recieve endocrine therapy? (No = 0, Yes = 1)
    • ChemoTrt: Did patient recieve chemotherapy? (No = 0, Yes = 1)
    • dfsTime: Disease-free survival time (years)
    • dfsEvent: Disease-free survival event (non-recurence=0, recurence=1)
    • dmfsTime: Distant-metastasis-free survival time (years)
    • dmfsEvent: Distant-metastasis-free survival event (no metastasis=0, metastasis=1)
    • dssTime: Disease-specific survival time (years)
    • dssEvent: Disease-specific survival event (alive=0, dead=1)

sampleDatap = sampleData[(sampleData$ER.status=="ER+" & sampleData$EndocrineTrt==1) ,]
sampleDatan = sampleData[(sampleData$ER.status=="ER-" & sampleData$PgR.status=="PgR-" & sampleData$EndocrineTrt==1),]
#dim(sampleDatan)
#sampleDatao = sampleDatap[(na.omit(sampleDatap$ER.status)),]

#expDatp = expDat[,(sampleDatap$sampleNames)]

#iqpif = ifelse(iqp > median(iqp), 1,0)

#mean(expDatp["IQSEC2",])
#median(expDatp["IQSEC2",])

#iqpp = expDatp["IQSEC2",]
#iqpp = as.matrix(iqpp)

sampleDataop = filter(sampleDatap, rowSums(is.na(sampleDatap)) != ncol(sampleDatap))
sampleDataon = filter(sampleDatan, rowSums(is.na(sampleDatan)) != ncol(sampleDatan))
expDatop = expDat[,sampleDataop$sampleNames]
expDaton = expDat[,sampleDataon$sampleNames]
IQSEC2pif = ifelse( expDatop["IQSEC2",] > mean(expDatop["IQSEC2",]), 1, 0)
table(IQSEC2pif)
## IQSEC2pif
##   0   1 
## 439 352
plot( survfit( Surv(sampleDataop$dmfsTime, sampleDataop$dmfsEvent) ~ IQSEC2pif ),
xlab = "Time in months", ylab = "Survival proportion", col = c(2,4))
legend('topright', c("IQSEC2 high", "IQSEC2 low"), fill = c('red', 'blue'))
